      <h4 align="left">Resources :</h4>
      <p class="intertitre">
      <img src="../images/images_pangloss/haut_parleur_s.png" alt="a" width="20" height="20"> <a href="../corpus/list_rsc_en.php?lg=Paicî&aff=Paicî" target="_blank"> All available resources here
